APNG Plug-In for GIMP
=====================

Copyright (C) 2010  Daisuke Nishikawa <daisuken@users.sourceforge.net>

This package is Animated PNG (APNG) plug-in for GIMP 2.x.

Quick build notes
=================

You need to have installed *patched* libpng.
Libpng can be downloaded from
	http://www.libpng.org/pub/png/libpng.html
	http://sourceforge.net/projects/libpng/

And you can get APNG patch from
	http://sourceforge.net/projects/libpng-apng/

Also you need to have installed GIMP version 2.4 or newer (2.6 or newer is
recommended) and GTK+ version 2.12 or newer.


